<CENTER><H1>Big Happy Family Magazine</H1></CENTER>
<IMG SRC="BHFcovers/BHF01cover.gif" ALT="Big Happy Family #1 cover">
<DL><DT>Yes, it's you! Disguised as a mild-mannered housewife or family man, you fight a 
never-ending battle for:<P>
<DD><B>Truth</B> ("Who drew the Mona Lisa on the living room wall?"), 
<BR><B>Justice</B> ("If you mess up, you clean up!"), and 
<BR><B>The American Way</B> ("Eat all your broccoli, Jimmy, or you might grow up to be President someday!"). 
</DL><P>

Nowadays even those who leap tall piles of dishes at a single bound could use a little 
extra help. And here it is! <P>

True stories, resources, humor, and encouragement for:<P>

<IMG SRC="redbullet.gif" ALIGN=bottom> pregnancy <IMG SRC="redbullet.gif" ALIGN=bottom> home birth <IMG SRC="redbullet.gif" ALIGN=bottom> breastfeeding 
