<CENTER><H1>Hands on Learning Fun</H1></CENTER>

<H2>THE GAMES</H2>
<DL>  
<DT><B>Card Games $11.95</B>
<DD>Playing non-gambling card games is a great way to make friends and develop thinking skills. 
This spiralbound book comes with affable instructions for the top 20 simple card games, plus 
a deluxe deck of cards. <B>#KCG</B><P>
  
<DT><B>Classic Board Games $17.95</B>
<DD>Everything you need to play 15 of the most popular board games of all time, including the 
playing pieces. Quality "board book" pages, lavishly illustrated.  <B>#KBG</B><P>
  
<DT><B>Jacks $8.95</B>
<DD>All-in-one package includes full-color, spiral-bound collection of 20 time-tested playground 
jacks games, PLUS a set of 14 painted jacks, a high-bounce rubber ball, and a drawstring 
fabric pouch for your ball and jacks. <B>#KJ</B><P>
  
