<DT><B>Knots $10.95</B>
<DD>You can't tie up a burglar with a granny knot. So why knot get this book and learn the basic 
knots you need in real life? This hands-on book comes with 4 feet of color-coded nylon cord. 
Its thick pages have die-cut holes, so you can practice tying 24 knots right in the book 
itself.  <B>#KK</B><P>
</DL>
