<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Juggling</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFF3B3>
<CENTER><H1>Juggling Equipment & Instruction</H1></CENTER>
    "Is your life low on
FUN, 
long on HOMEWORK
and HOUSEWORK?
    "Then you're like I used to be . . . before I discovered 
the joy of 
Juggling!"

Juggling can . . .<P>
<UL>
<LI>Unwind those tense nerves!<BR>
<LI>Increase your physical dexterity!<BR>
<LI>Improve your upper body strength and lung capacity!<BR>
<LI>Unlock "mental blocks" that interfere with those great grades Mom and Dad expect of you!<BR>
<LI>Make you COOL and POPULAR!<P>
</UL>

Juggling is the ideal homeschool sport. Just consider the alternatives. Can you play hockey, 
baseball, or basketball in your living room? Can you become an accomplished figure skater 
or skier for just pennies a day? Can you play polo or rugby in front of cheering crowds 
without having to buy a whole wardrobe of fancy shirts? And when times are tough, have you 
ever seen someone throwing a football back and forth on a street corner, with a hat on the 
ground beside him, and people throwing money into the hat? <P>

All ages can juggle alone or in teams. Unlike tiddlywinks, juggling is real cardiovascular 
exercise, too. Even kids with one hand and adults in wheelchairs can juggle! <P>

"I know what you're saying. I can't learn to juggle. It's too hard.' <BR>
"Go ahead, let everyone else keep thinking that. They'll be amazed by your skills. Now 
I'm going to tell you the secret of learning to juggle. . . ."<P>

You start with <B>colorful scarves</B>. Regular scarves won't doyou need our special light, rip-resistant 
Juggling Scarves. They float in the air when you toss them, so you learn to juggle in slow motion. 
<B>#JSC, just $9 for a set of three scarves and instructions</B>.<P>

Next, you need our <B>Juggling Step-by-Step video</B>. Produced by award-winning juggling instructor Dave 
Finnegan, this two-hour VHS tape takes you from scarf juggling, to balls and beanbags, rings, clubs, 
rhythm sticks, diabolos, and even flaming torches! It's like one full year of personal juggling 
instruction! This video was a steal at <B>$49.</B> Now it's an even better deal at just $29. Dave sold his 
juggling company, and we don't know how long this tape will be available, so order NOW to avoid 
disappointment. <B>#JLV</B><P>

We know you're anxious to start "real" juggling with beanbags or balls. <B>Our Fancy European Beanballs</B> 
give you the best of both worlds. Super tough skin, glowing colors, perfect spheres that fly through 
the air with the greatest of ease. To squeeze them is to love them. <B>$19 for a set of 3</B>. Let us choose 
the colors for you. <B>#JBB</B><P>

You'll be ready to "join the clubs" sooner than you think with our <B>Soft & Safe Clubs!</B> Perfectly weighted 
and pretty, too! <B>$35 for a set of 3. #JCL</B><P>

SAVE with these special deals: <B>Juggling Starter Kit</B> includes scarves, video, and beanballs, <B>#JSK, $55</B>. 
<B>Deluxe Kit</B> has it all: scarves, video, beanballs, AND clubs, <B>#JDK, $89</B>.<P>

Terrific birthday giftsa lifetime of fun and exercise for just pennies a day!<P>

