<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Diapers</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFF3B3>
<H1>Squeezably Soft Diapers</H1>

Hi! I'm Mary Pride. As the mother of nine children, I've tried just about every type of diaper 
over the years. Gauze. Birdseye. Flat. Folded. Padded. Lined. Velcro. Attached covers. You name it!

<H2>None of them satisfied me.</H2>

For one thing, they weren't absorbent enough. I don't know about you, but I'm tired of double- 
and triple-diapering my kids.<P>

For another thing, they weren't durable enough. A good diaper 
should last through baby after baby, not give up the ghost after a few months of laundering.<P>

And they should not require fancy care (ever try cleaning a stool off a diaper with an attached cover? Yuk!).

<H2>The Ultimate Diaper</H2>

As you may have guessed, I finally found what I was looking for. Superabsorbent. 100% cotton. 
So soft they are squeezable! The best diaper services use these diapers. Each contains as much 
cotton as two or even three cheaper diapers, so you don't need as many. These diapers are easy to 
use, easy to store, and easy to wash.<P>

And we offer a <B>ONE YEAR WEAR GUARANTEE</B> on every set of diapers 
you buy from us!<P>
Dozen small diapers, <B>#DIPES, $20</B>. Dozen large, <B>#DIPEL, $25</B>.<BR>
Sampler pak of 2 dipes (specify size), <B>$5 (#PAK).</B> Sorry, sampler paks 
are not returnable. 
