http://www.home-school.com:80/Articles/OnlineAtTheLibrary.HTML 205.186.59.2 19970216065528 text/html 13482
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/2015
Message-ID: <af2c0b06.57517@www.home-school.com>
