<br>Originally published in Practical Homeschooling No. 4. 
<br>All rights reserved. This article or any part of it may not be published on any Internet or WWW site, or any BBS, or any other electronic or print medium, or any other medium, without our expression written permission. To request permission, please fax 314-225-0743 and describe the article, where you would like to publish it, and how many people you expect to read your publication. We will get back to you with our response as soon as possible.
</body>

