<DOCOLDNO>IA084-000597-B031-364</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.home-school.com:80/Articles/ImproveWriting.HTML 205.186.59.2 19970216065757 text/html 12742
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/2015
Message-ID: <af2c0ba0.57534@www.home-school.com>
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 06:56:00 GMT
