<H1><CENTER>Homeschool Organization Information Sheet</CENTER><HR size="3"></H1>
<B><Font size="+2">I</Font></B>f you represent a state or national homeschool organization and would like to take advantage of your organization's <strong>free page</strong> on Homeschool World, please fill in the following information and click the <B>Submit Info</B> button.  We will format the information and put it online so people can find your group more easily.
<form METHOD=POST ACTION="mailto:HSorgs@home-school.com">
Organization Name:<Input Type="text" Name="name" size="42"><BR>
Organization Address 1:<Input Type="text" Name="address1" size="39"><BR>
Organization Address 2:<Input Type="text" Name="address2" size="39"><BR>
Organization City:<Input Type="text" Name="city" size="20"> State:<Input Type="text" Name="state" size="2"> Zip:<Input Type="text" Name="zip" size="10"><BR>
Organization Country:<Input Type="text" Name="country" size="25"><BR>
Phone number for new contacts:<Input type="text" Name="phone" size="17"><BR>
What is the legal situation for homeschoolers in your state:<BR>
<Textarea Name="LegalInfo" Rows=3 Cols=30></Textarea><P>
Other info to include (For example, Contact person, Contact phone, convention date/speakers/location/last years attendance/Price/who to contact/how was it last year?:<BR>
<Textarea Name="OtherInfo" Rows=3 Cols=30></Textarea><BR>
<H2>Thanks! <input type="submit" value="Send Info"><input type="reset" value="Clear Form"> </H2></form>
<B><Font size="+2">I</Font></B>f you have the text of your homeschool law we would be glad to include it under your state's page. If you have it in electronic form or could type it in for us, we would be very grateful. Please e-mail it to Bill@home-school.com. If not, please snail mail it to Bill Pride, Home Life, Inc., 1731 Smizer Mill Rd., Fenton, MO 63026-2635.<P>
<B><Font size="+2">I</Font></B>f for any reason the submit button brings up a generic mail screen this will mean the form is not working for your browser. Please enter the information we requested as a message and send it on to Bill@home-school.com. Thanks!<P>
