<TITLE>Link</TITLE>
<BODY BACKGROUND="Http://www.home-school.com/homepage/homebkgrnd.GIF">
<CENTER><H1>What is a Nonreciprocal Link?</H1></CENTER>
Add a link from our site to yours and watch traffic build! If you don't want to place a link
to Homeschool World on your home page, choose our "nonreciprocal link" option. To do so, just
fill out the <A HREF="Insertion.HTML">order form</A> and either provide credit card info
or include a check for the desired term of service.<P>
