<TITLE>Reciprocal Link</TITLE>
<BODY BACKGROUND="Http://www.home-school.com/homepage/homebkgrnd.GIF">
<CENTER><H2>What is a Reciprocal Link?</H2></CENTER>
Add a link from our site to yours and watch traffic build! The most inexpensive option is our "reciprocal link."
It's called "reciprocal" because you agree to add a link from your home page to our home page (reciprocating
our links). A small additional fee ($99/6 months, $199/year) is also required. We will check
your site to see if the reciprocal link is up after we have received payment and put up your
link.<P>
To sign up for a reciprocal link to Homeschool World, place this HTML text on your home page:<P>
Other Sites of Interest&LT;BR&GT;<BR>
&LT;A HREF="Http://www.home-school.com"&GT;Homeschool World&LT;/A&GT; Lots of good articles about
home education, plus access to the latest products, groups, and events. Sponsored by Practical Homeschooling and Homeschool PC magazines.<P>
Text on this page copyright 1997 Home Life, Inc. All rights reserved.<P>
Return to the <A HREF="Insertion.HTML">order form</A>. Return to the <A HREF="HTTP://WWW.Home-School.COM/HsMall.HTML">Homeschool Mall</A>.
