<TITLE>What is a Classified Ad?</TITLE>
<BODY BACKGROUND="Http://www.home-school.com/homepage/homebkgrnd.GIF">
<CENTER><H1>What is a Classified Ad?</H1></CENTER>
A classified ad is a simple advertisement with up to 50 words and one picture. When it is approved it will be added to the Homeschool World <A HREF="http://www.home-school.com/Mall/Classifieds/Classifieds.html">classifieds page</A>.<P>
