<TITLE>Keywords</TITLE>
<BODY BACKGROUND="Http://www.home-school.com/homepage/homebkgrnd.GIF">
<CENTER><H1>What is a "Keyword"?</H1></CENTER>
Keywords are words that tell what your page is about.<BR>
Suppose you had a page about antique automobiles (though realistically, you probably don't.)<BR>
You might use the keywords <B>car, auto, automobile, vehicle, classic, antique, old, vintage, Chevy, and Ford</B>.<BR>
If you had a page advertising cassettes to improve grammar you would perhaps have the first couple keywords be your company's name and you could use <B>tape, cassette, audio, grammar, english, and writing</B> for the rest.
<P>
Text on this page copyright 1997 Home Life, Inc. All rights reserved.<P>
Return to the <A HREF="Insertion.HTML">order form</A>. Return to the <A HREF="HTTP://WWW.Home-School.COM/HsMall.HTML">Homeschool Mall</A>.
