<TITLE>Practical Homeschooling Media Kit</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFCC>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="PHSLogo.GIF"><HR>
<A HREF="#Facts">Frequently Asked Questions</A><BR>
<A HREF="#Terms">Practical Homeschooling Advertising Terms and Conditions</A><HR></CENTER>
Thank you for inquiring about advertising in PRACTICAL HOMESCHOOLING!<P>
Here's a fun fact you may find interesting: Homeschoolers are the most motivated buyers of educational products around. The total homeschool market now approaches <B>$1 BILLION</B> in annual sales!<P>
<B>We have the homeschool readers you are looking for.</B><P>
<B>Homeschoolers are excellent customers for educational products.</B> In fact, surveys show that the average homeschool family spends 16 TIMES more on educational materials per child than the average local school district does!<P>
Because of their great concern for family life, homeschoolers also are exceptionally strong buyers of <B>books, health products, baby and family products,</B> and quality <B>toys and games.</B> These are just a <I>few</I> of the products that homeschoolers are snapping up!<P>
If you're not in this market already, <B>you should be!</B> And, with all the services we can offer your company, <B>we're the best place to start.</B><P>
Consider us as part of your marketing team--<B>we want to help you succeed.</B> Just tell us what you want your ad to say and we'll design and typeset it for FREE! We'll even help with rewording and marketing advice, upon request, for FREE!<P>
Any questions? Just call and ask. We will be happy to explain our services and how we can help you succeed in the homeschool market.<P>
Yours truly,<BR>
<IMG SRC="Signature.GIF"><BR>
Mary Pride, Publisher<P>

P.S. With our new <B>lower ad rates,</B> remaining ad space in PRACTICAL HOMESCHOOLING will soon be gone. So don't delay -- <B>fax or mail us your ad TODAY!</B><HR>
<CENTER>1731 Smizer Mill Road, Fenton, MO, 63026-2635 - Tel: 314.343.6786 - Fax: 314.225.0743</CENTER><HR>

