<dl>
<dt><strong>Newsletter:</strong>
<dd>CHEO's newsletter, <em>The Ohio Home School Companion</em> comes out bi-monthly. 16 pages. Good mixture of legislative news, support group info, how to's and inspirational articles.<p>
