<TITLE>Titan - Crius</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="000000" TEXT="FFFFFF" LINK="E02020" VLINK="C65050">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="titans.gif"><p>
<HR><P>
<H1><B>Crius</H1></B><P>   Crius was a Titan, one of the sons of Gaea (Mother Earth) and Uranus (Sky).  There were various rivers named after him, including the river of Achaia and a river on Mt. Sipylus.  His children were Astraeus, Pallas and Perses.
<P><HR><P>
