<TITLE>Titan - Iapetus</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="000000" TEXT="FFFFFF" LINK="E02020" VLINK="C65050">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="titans.gif"><p>
<HR><P>
<H1><B>Iapetus</H1></B><P>   Iapetus was the father of Atlas, Prometheus, Epimetheus and Menoetius by Asia.  He is also said to have had a son, Buphagus, by someone called Thornax. (Which, by the way, is another name for the cuckoo.)
<P><HR><P>
