<TITLE>Some of my Artwork</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#000000 TEXT=#00FF00 LINK=#FFFF00 VLINK=#FF0000>
<CENTER><H1>Some of my Artwork</H1></CENTER>

I draw simply as a hobby. I like doing it, that's all the motivation I have. It's enough.<BR>
In all my art I only have a few pictures I spent enough time on to make into masterpieces,
but here's a couple of them. Practically every picture I have drawn was done with colored pencils.<P>
<A HREF="Lady.JPG">A pretty lady, always a challenge for any artist.</A><BR>
<A HREF="Saturday.JPG">A typical summer activity in the suburbs; cleaning a car that's already
perfect.</A><P>

If you'd like to see more, perhaps a photo of one of my 3D creations, well, I'll get to
that in a bit.<P>

