<TITLE>Joseph Pride's Homepage</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#000000 TEXT=#00FF00 LINK=#FFFF00 VLINK=#FF0000>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="JoesPage.GIF"></CENTER><BR>
Welcome to my own little square inch of the Web! My name is Joseph Pride, as shown in
45-point type on that heading. I designed this page with a text editor, available wherever
good computers are sold, and I created the graphics with Adobe Photoshop, available for
major $$$$$ from just about every major Macintosh software catalog. I'm lucky I need it
for my job, otherwise I would have had to buy it myself! You can e-mail me at
<A HREF="Mailto:Joseph@Home-School.COM">Joseph@home-school.com</A>.<P>

I'm a 15-year old Christian homeschooled kid from Missouri. I'm 5'10" high (last I measured),
I weigh 170 lb, I have brown hair and blue eyes and that just about covers it. I make
Web ads for my work and I play outside or on the computer for my fun.<P>
<A HREF="Pics.HTML">Whatever pictures of me I've managed to compile, don't expect much
for a while.</A><BR>
<A HREF="Friends.HTML">My friends online. This page will be constantly changing.</A><BR>
<A HREF="Games.HTML">My favorite games for the Mac</A><BR>
<A HREF="Art.HTML">Some of my artwork</A><BR>
<A HREF="T4J.HTML">#Teens4Jesus, my FAVORITE place to chat.</A><P>
<B>AND NOW</B> (drumroll)<BR>
<CENTER><A HREF="Harkin.HTML"><IMG SRC="Harkin.GIF"></A></CENTER>
My IRC persona. Who the heck is the lieutenant, and what are those weird Fists of Fury
things?<P>

