<TITLE>#Teens4jesus</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#000000 TEXT=#00FF00 LINK=#FFFF00 VLINK=#FF0000>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="T4J.JPG"></CENTER>
#Teens4jesus is <B>the</B> best Christian chat room on the DALnet. A place where Christian
teenagers can meet <B>other</B> Christian teenagers on the Net. And if you're not a teenager
feel free to chat a bit anyways. Sure, parents are welcome too!<P>

You'll meet some <B>really</B> wonderful people out here, guaranteed! Practically all
my friends online chat here.<P>

Chat room policy:<BR>
Offensive nicknames will result in a warning kick and a request to change the nickname.
Should you not change the nickname you will be banned.<BR>
Profanity and vulgarity will result in instant ban/kick.<BR>
Please do not ask
for ops; you must earn them by becoming a trusted regular. Only <A HREF="http://www.mcmsys.com/~sandys/index.htm">Gracie</A> can give ops, being
the channel's founder and supreme operator.<BR>
<I>Keep America's chat rooms clean!</I> :-)
</DOC>
